place.name: INVERKEITHNY
place.gazetteerText: Inverkeithny, par. and vil., Banff shire - par., 7641 ac., pop. 909; vil., on river Deveron, 7 miles SW. of Turriff; P.O. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
